### Create Task in Organization
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/organizations/{{organizationId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "First Task",
  "description": "Create initial task",
  "status": "todo",
  "assignedTo": {{userBId}}
}

### List Organization Tasks
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/organizations/{{organizationId}}/tasks
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE>

### Update Task
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/organizations/{{organizationId}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "in-progress",
  "description": "Started working"
}

### Delete Task (admin only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/organizations/{{organizationId}}/tasks/{{taskId}}
Authorization: Bearer <PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE>

### Refresh Access Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "<PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE>"
}

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "<PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE>"
}
